  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multiplatform development (JVM, JS, WasmJS, Android, iOS)",
    "Built-in reliability and fault-tolerance with retries and persistence",
    "Intelligent history compression for token optimization",
    "Enterprise integrations with Spring Boot and Ktor",
    "OpenTelemetry support for observability",
    "Multiple LLM provider support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, Ollama, etc.)",
    "Type-safe Kotlin DSL for agent configuration",
    "Model Context Protocol (MCP) integration",
    "Agent Client Protocol (ACP) support",
    "Advanced features: memory, RAG, embeddings",
    "Graph-based workflows for complex agent behaviors",
    "Comprehensive testing utilities",
    "Streaming API with parallel tool calls"
  ],
